sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant AGW as Agentgateway Proxy
    participant API as Upstream API

    Client->>AGW: Request + Authorization: Bearer OIDC-JWT
    AGW->>AGW: 1. Validate JWT (jwtAuthentication)
    AGW->>AGW: 2. Extract claim (e.g. jwt.sub, jwt.team)
    AGW->>AGW: 3. CEL transformation:<br/>jwt.team == engineering<br/>then opaque-token-eng<br/>else opaque-token-default
    AGW->>API: Request + Authorization: Bearer mapped-opaque-token
    API-->>AGW: Response
    AGW-->>Client: Response
